OL,6,FA man who was helped by his girlfriend
OL,7,Fto flee the country after ordering a
OL,8,Fshooting which killed a young father
OL,9,Fhas been jailed for at least 33 years.
OL,11,FEthan Hallows flew to Dubai following
OL,12,Fthe murder of 19-year-old Kevin Pokuta
OL,13,Fin a case of mistaken identity in
OL,14,FSheffield, in December 2023.
OL,16,FEvidence later found on the phone of
OL,17,Fhis partner Paris Askew showed she had
OL,18,Fsearched the internet for information
OL,19,Fabout extradition treaties and
OL,20,FInterpol's "wanted" list as the couple
OL,21,Fplotted a life abroad.
