OL,3,CBotched hit-job killer jailed along
OL,4,Cwith girlfriend who helped him flee
OL,6,FHallows, 25, of Oxford Street,
OL,7,FSheffield, denied murder but was found
OL,8,Fguilty after a trial at Sheffield
OL,9,FCrown Court and jailed for life with a
OL,10,Fminimum 33-year term.
OL,12,FAskew, 23, of Griffiths Road,
OL,13,FSheffield, was found guilty of
OL,14,Fassisting an offender and jailed for
OL,15,Fthree years.
OL,17,FMr Pokuta was shot dead as he sat in a
OL,18,Fcar on Page Hall Road, Sheffield, in
OL,19,Fthe early hours of 12 December 2023 in
OL,20,Fa case of mistaken identity.
