OL,3,CBotched hit-job killer jailed along
OL,4,Cwith girlfriend who helped him flee
OL,6,FThe court heard he was attacked in a
OL,7,Frevenge mission by Hallows and his
OL,8,Fassociates after they had carried out
OL,9,Fa failed robbery at a cannabis farm
OL,10,Fthe previous night.
OL,12,FJake Brown carried out the fatal
OL,13,Fshooting after Hallows wrongly
OL,14,Fidentified Mr Pokuta's car as having
OL,15,Fbeen driven at them in the earlier
OL,16,Fincident.
OL,18,FJake Brown carried out the shooting
OL,19,Fafter mistaking Kevin Pokuta for a
OL,20,Fgang rival
