OL,3,CBotched hit-job killer jailed along
OL,4,Cwith girlfriend who helped him flee
OL,6,FJudge Recorder Jeremy Richardson KC
OL,7,Ftold Hallows: "(Brown) executed what
OL,8,Fyou had directed."
OL,10,FThe day after the murder Hallows was
OL,11,Fseen on CCTV being dropped off at
OL,12,FManchester Airport to fly to Dubai.
OL,14,FScreenshots found on Askew's phone
OL,15,Fshowed she had sent Hallows
OL,16,Finformation about the police
OL,17,Finvestigation and carried out searches
OL,18,Fabout which countries did not have
OL,19,Fextradition agreements with the UK.
