OL,3,CBotched hit-job killer jailed along
OL,4,Cwith girlfriend who helped him flee
OL,6,FHallows was arrested when he flew back
OL,7,Fto England in May last year.
OL,9,FAs well as murder he was found guilty
OL,10,Fof conspiracy to rob, possession of a
OL,11,Ffirearm with intent to endanger life
OL,12,Fand attempting to cause grievous
OL,13,Fbodily harm with intent.
OL,15,FBrown is already serving a life
OL,16,Fsentence for murder. Four others were
OL,17,Fconvicted of conspiracy to commit
OL,18,Frobbery.
