OL,3,CBotched hit-job killer jailed along
OL,4,Cwith girlfriend who helped him flee
OL,6,FDet Ch Insp Tom Woodward, of South
OL,7,FYorkshire Police, said: "Hallows'
OL,8,Fcowardly conduct saw him run away to
OL,9,Favoid facing the consequences of his
OL,10,Factions.
OL,12,F"We have no place for gun crime in
OL,13,FSouth Yorkshire. Lives such as Kevin's
OL,14,Fand his family's, are often ruined and
OL,15,Fwe will continue to investigate,
OL,16,Farrest and prosecute those who choose
OL,17,Fto bring gun violence to our streets."
